results.name: First digit of tribonacci sequence A000213.
comment: Sequence obeys the Benford law about distribution of first digit d in a sequence: P(d) = log_10(1+1/d).
link: Index entries for sequences related to Benford's law
mathematica: t = {1,1,1}; Do[AppendTo[t, t[[-1]] + t[[-2]] + t[[-3]]], {100}]; Table[IntegerDigits[i][[1]], {i, t}]
